Using curl to fetch your publuc ip:
curl -s https://api.ipify.org?format=json

Using curl -I to get headers from three different sites:
curl -I https://www.google.com -s; echo; curl -I https://github.com -s; echo; curl -I https://example.com -s

Creating downloads/ and use wget -P downloads/ <url> to save a file:
mkdir -p downloads
wget -P downloads/ https://example.com -q -O downloads/example.html || true; ls -l downloads